    <p class="text-black font-bold">For questions or appointments <a href="https://www.instagram.com/bastianteeuwen/" class="text-blue-700 underline hover:no-underline">DM on Instagram</a> or <a href="#contactForm" class="text-blue-700 underline hover:no-underline">email.</p>
